# compiled Metal libraries, keyed by the emitted source's own sha256 (regenerable
# in seconds; the emitted source is the artifact, not the binary)
.metallib-cache/

# the body's answers about a FIXED blob through FIXED cells: config, tensor table,
# the 128 256-piece tokenizer, the emitted MSL and the fp64 references. ~13 MB,
# keyed by sha256(cells + blob identity) so a changed recipe is a cache MISS by
# construction. Regenerable in ~90 s; never committed, because it is a derivative
# of a 2 GB model file that is not in this repo either.
.first-token-cache/

# the body's ONE header walk over the ds4 file's 1406 tensor-info rows (~22 s),
# keyed by sha256 of the header bytes themselves, so a different file or a moved
# tensor is a cache MISS by construction. Never committed: it is a derivative of
# an 85 GiB model file that is not in this repo.
.mx-table-cache/
